      "title": "Ordinals 11-19",
      "titleArabic": "التَّرْتِيبِيَّةُ مِنْ 11-19",
      "content": [
        "For 11-19, the first part uses ordinal form and the second is عَشَر (m) or عَشْرَة (f). Both parts agree with the noun in gender (unlike cardinals!).",
