      "title": "Gender Agreement",
      "titleArabic": "الْمُطَابَقَةُ فِي الْجِنْسِ",
      "content": [
        "Ordinal numbers AGREE with their noun in gender (unlike cardinal numbers 3-10 which reverse). This is because ordinals function as adjectives (صفات), not as counted nouns.",
